missionEventData.data1: All craft prepare to jump on my mark.
There's the Convoy. The defectors have assured us that the Corvettes lasers have been disabled.
Red01 take out the Arreis. Red01 and Red02 focus on the Orcim and the Esorp.

Alliance intelligence reports that the crew of the Imperial Corvette Bixby wish to defect. The Corvette is currently escorting an Imperial convoy through the Dellalt system. X-Wings from Red Squadron will jump in to destroy the Imperial freighters before the transport Dagger boards to help the crew secure the vessel. Be on your guard for any Imperial interference.
The transport Dagger is jumping in to secure the Bixby.
The Dagger has completed docking and is reporting resistance on board the vessel.
Warning! An Imperial Frigate is exiting Hyperspace.
The Frigate is launching Ties. You need to give the Dagger more time.
The ship has been secured. Keep those Ties engaged while the Bixby and the Dagger move the to the jump point.
We've secured the Bixby. Make your escape to the jump point.

missionEventData.data2: It is a period of Civil War. Using fear and intimidation, the Empire seeks to impose a New Order on the galaxy. Only the Rebel Alliance stands in the way of their evil plans. Not yet willing to confront the Empire directly, the Rebels are marshalling their forces in secrecy. Even now a group of their prized Calamari Cruisers is being intercepted by a squadron of Imperial Star Destroyers. The Rebel Fleet is outnumbered but, they have a surprise… the X-Wing Starfighter!
